Job Description
Job Description:Should have hands on experience either on Oracle Revenue Mgmt and Billing (RMB) or Customer Credit and Billing (CC&B) application.Should have sound understanding of the functional working of CCB/RMB product.Should understand RMB for Finance/Insurance.Should know the technical architecture of the product.Should have knowledge on critical setups, and typical extensions needed for implementation.Should be able to assist batch runs, jobs etc within RMB.Should be knowledgeable with at least 3 of the following: UI configuration, zones, interfacing to RMB/CCB, extending algorithms.Strong communication & inter-personal skills.Nice to have skills:At least one full cycle implementation OR more than 6 months of RMB/CCB support.Flexibility & openness to learn new modules
